title: Average price for a full set of acrylics at nail salons in the U.S. 2006 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Average price in U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 14.
In general Average price in U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Average price in U.S. dollars, about 50.1 was reported at Year 2008
The lowest Average price in U.S. dollars, of value 38.41 was reported at Year 2016
